    <div class="Water">    
        <h3 style=" font-size: 30px; text-align: left; color: white;"><strong><i>Water Requirement:</i></strong></h3>             
            <p style="color: white;font-size: 20px;">Papaya needs regular water for its rapid fruit development and yield. During summer months, the plants should be given 20-25 L of water and can be gradually reduced to 10-15 L of water/plant in winter. Drip irrigation helps to save 50-60% water. Irrigation through drip @ 6-8 L/day/plant gives better yields.
            </p>
